0.headline: Billy Joe Saunders eyes Saul 'Canelo' Alvarez after Marcelo Esteban Coceres win - BBC News
0.description: Billy Joe Saunders defends his world super-middleweight title with victory over Marcelo Esteban Coceres and targets Saul 'Canelo' Alvarez.

1.headline: 'Berlin Candy Bomber' honoured as UK mourns war dead on Remembrance Sunday - Sky News
1.description: The 99-year-old received a standing ovation while on stage with a woman who was one of the children he helped during a blockade.

2.headline: KSI v Logan Paul 2: KSI wins on split decision in Youtubers' contest - BBC News
2.description: British Youtuber KSI beats Logan Paul on a split decision at the Staples Center in Los Angeles.

3.headline: General Election: Claims on Labour spending should be viewed with caution - Sky News
3.description: The costings splashed across Sunday's newspapers are not from Labour's manifesto because it has yet to be published.
